title: Toast Five Points Durham
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Italian, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Panini, bruschetta, crostini, and sandwiches. Uses farm sourced, local and seasonal produce. Menu changes with whatever is fresh. Always a vegetarian soup daily. Participated in Durhams'first Vegan Challenge 2010 and supports the local economy and revitalization of downtown Durham.
